                       new { value = "5"  , text = "More bosses and world events"  },
                       new { value = "6"  , text = "Mind-control type transformation"  },
                       new { value = "7"  , text = "Absorption type transformation"  },

                    },
                  "value",
                  "text",
                   2))
    
    <hr />
    
    <p>What game mechanic would you like to see added first?  (Second preference).  Please do not duplicate the answer selected above.</p>
